          <view class="price">￥99</view>
          <view class="count">X1</view>
        </view>
      </view>
      <view class="ord-item">
        <image class="thumbnail" src="../../../images/p1.png"></image>
        <view class="con lineText2">宏辉果蔬 苹果 烟台红富士 12个 单果约75mm 总重约2.1kg 新鲜水果</view>
